      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** +--- Start of Main processing -------------------------------+
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** ¦ *INZSR is executed at program activation.                  ¦
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** +------------------------------------------------------------+
      *
      ** Initialise work variables.
     C                   EVAL      IDx = 0
      *
      ** Initialise variables for update of Valid File fields.
     C                   EVAL      WInitPr = 0
      *
      ** Validate initial payment
      *
     C                   EXSR      SRValIPymnt
      *
      ** If an error has been found, set return code appropriately.
      ** Otherwise, update valid file fields.
      *
     C                   IF        OKSINP = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      RetCodeIn = 'ERROR'
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   IF        OKSINP <> 'N'
     C                   Z-ADD     WInitPr       S1SINP

     C                   IF        DDACTN = 'I'
     C                   Z-ADD     S1SINP        S1CPDP
     C                   Z-ADD     S1SINP        S1TPHD
     C                   ELSE
     C                   IF        S1INCS = 'C' AND ODDINCS = 'I'
     C                   Z-ADD     S1SINP        S1CPDP
     C                   Z-ADD     S1SINP        S1TPHD
     C                   ENDIF
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDIF

     C                   RETURN
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRVALIPYMNT - Validation for Initial Payment                 *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C     SRValIPymnt   BEGSR
      *
      ** Initial paid prices are based on 3 decimal places if processing
      ** type is not '4', else nominal currency decimal place is used
      *
     C                   IF        DDSINP <> *BLANKS
      *
      ** Check valid number
     C                   MOVEL     *BLANKS       ZFIELD
     C                   MOVEL     DDSINP        ZFIELD

     C                   IF        PPROT <> '4'
     C                   Z-ADD     3             ZADIG
     C                   Z-ADD     3             ZADEC
     C                   CALLB     'ZALIGN'
     C                   PARM                    ZALIGNok
     C                   PARM                    ZFIELD
     C                   PARM                    ZADEC
     C                   PARM                    ZADIG

     C                   IF        ZALIGNok = 'N'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKSINP
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDSINP'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0222'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVE      ZFIELD        WInitPr
     C                   MOVE      ZFIELD        Work6N
     C                   IF        Work6N >= 100
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKSINP
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDSINP'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0222'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   ENDIF
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ELSE
      *
      ** Check valid number
     C     15            SUB       PNmDp         ZADIG
     C                   Z-ADD     PNmDp         ZADEC
     C                   CALLB     'ZALIGN'
     C                   PARM                    ZALIGNok
     C                   PARM                    ZFIELD
     C                   PARM                    ZADEC
     C                   PARM                    ZADIG

     C                   IF        ZALIGNok = 'N'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKSINP
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDSINP'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0223'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVE      ZFIELD        WInitPr
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDIF
      *
      ** Else if blank and security is complete, error
     C                   ELSE

     C                   IF        S1INCS = 'C'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKSINP
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDSINP'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   IF        PPROT <> '4'
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0222'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0223'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   ENDIF
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *INZSR - Program Initialisation                              *
      *         - This subroutine runs automatically for program      *
      *           initialisation.                                     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
      *
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
      *
      ** INPUT
      ** =====
      *
      ** Return code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
      *
      ** Securities screen 1 details from incoming transaction
      ** - screen format
     C                   PARM                    NwSE1ScnFmt
      *
      ** Securities screen 1 details retrieved from file
      ** - screen format
     C                   PARM                    CrSE1ScnFmt
      *
      ** Securities screen 2 details from incoming transaction
      ** - screen format
     C                   PARM                    NwSE2ScnFmt
      *
      ** Processing type, from PF/INVTPD
     C                   PARM                    PPROT
      *
      ** Nominal ccy no. of decimal places
     C                   PARM                    PNmDp
      *
      ** OUTPUT
      ** ======
      *
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Securities screen 2 error indicators
     C                   PARM                    SEESEC2
      *
      ** Securities for file update - file format
     C                   PARM                    NwSEFilFmt
      *
      ** Program, module and procedure names for dbase error processing
      ** ==============================================================
      ** The following /COPY sets these values.
      *
      /COPY ZACPYSRC,DBFIELDS
      *
     C                   ENDSR
